(22944, 'Montel 10mg 10 f.c. tab.', 'مونتيل 10مجم 10 اقراص', '36', '46', 'Montelukast', 'Pharopharma > ema pharm', 'Tab', 'أقراص', '', 'Asthma.anti-inflammatory.leukotriene antagonist', '10mg', 'Montelukast is indicated for:
